subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king is associated with the famous 1825 Treaty of Longawai?
question_hi: कौन सा राज्य के चार्मा के 1825 को सूचीबद्ध संदेश कामंडन के नामक 'लॉंगावाई केवल टीज़र' के विशेष प्रश्न
explanation_en: Maharaja Pratap Singh is associated with the Treaty of Longowal, which was signed in 1843 between the British East India Company and the Rathore dynasty. King Maharaja Ganga Singh is known for his role in the Punjab Rebellion of 1857, not for the Treaty of Longowal.
